850
00:39:14,500 --> 00:39:16,100
Honey, i know.

851
00:39:16,100 --> 00:39:18,700
I love this place, too.

852
00:39:18,700 --> 00:39:21,300
I just -- i think it's time
For us to face the music.

853
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:36,100
[ sighs ]

854
00:39:42,100 --> 00:39:47,200
I never thought i'd be poor
At this stage of my life.

855
00:39:47,200 --> 00:39:49,400
You know, carlos,

