00:41:06,900 --> 00:41:09,100
Now...

881
00:41:09,100 --> 00:41:12,000
Let's talk about what's going
To make you happy.

882
00:41:18,700 --> 00:41:21,800
Mary alice: yes,
Each new day in suburbia

883
