We tell ourselves

885
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:30,600
Before we fall asleep.

886
00:41:30,600 --> 00:41:32,800
We whisper them in the dark,

887
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:34,900
Telling ourselves...

888
00:41:34,900 --> 00:41:37,600
We're happy.

889
00:41:37,600 --> 00:41:39,500
Or...

890
00:41:39,500 --> 00:41:44,700
That he's happy.

891
00:41:44,700 --> 00:41:49,900
That we can change.

892
00:41:49,900 --> 00:41:53,800
Or that he will change
His mind.

893
00:41:58,100 --> 00:42:03,000
We persuade ourselves
We can live with our sins...

894
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:16,200
Or that we can live
Without him.

895
00:42:16,200 --> 00:42:19,900
Yes, each night
Before we fall asleep,

896
00:42:19,900 --> 00:42:22,100
We lie to ourselves

